edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits

Class XmlContentConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits.XmlContentConverter

  • public class XmlContentConverter
extends Object
    This class handles conversion between FITS metadata and XmlContent implementations of metadata schemas. ots-schemas.jar (or the OTS-Schemas project in Eclipse) has to be on the build path for this to compile.
